Generic single-database configuration with async support.

This configuration uses SQLAlchemy with async support for database migrations.

## 使用方法

### 生成新迁移
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "描述变更"
```

### 执行迁移
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### 回滚迁移
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### 查看当前版本
```bash
alembic current
```

### 查看迁移历史
```bash
alembic history
```

